file.name: pingSomeObj.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: ping some object
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:8082/'
paths:
  /ping:
    post:
      operationId: postPing
      tags:
      - ping
      requestBody:
        content:
          'application/json':
             schema:
               $ref: "#/components/schemas/SomeObj"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            'application/json':
               schema:
                 $ref: "#/components/schemas/SomeObj"
components:
  schemas:
    SomeObj:
      type: object
      properties:
        $_type:
          type: string
          # using 'enum' & 'default' for '$_type' is a work-around until constants are supported
          # See https://github.com/OAI/OpenAPI-Specification/issues/1313
          enum:
          - SomeObjIdentifier
          default: SomeObjIdentifier
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        name:
          type: string
        active:
          type: boolean
        type:
          type: string
